If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email : office@alecoair.ro
AlecoAir products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or change settings. 

After connecting Alexa to your AlecoAir Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "AlecoAir" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one AlecoAir Smart account in our "AlecoAir" app;
(3). You need to have some AlecoAir Smart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our AlecoAir Smart" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "AlecoAir Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "AlecoAir Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "AlecoAir Smart", and you'll be navigated to AlecoAir login page;
(9). Input your AlecoAir account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices

Alexa, turn on air purifier
Alexa: turn off air purifier
